According the Daily Mail, hoax-haunted Jussie Smollett has lost a lead role in the Broadway show Take Me Out.
Jussie was in the running for the part, but the outlet confirmed he’s been nixed from consideration.
Charges against the actor were recently dropped, but that did little to make things hunky dory (here, here, here, and here).
“He would have come off the sixth season of Empire and kicked off the next leg of his career with a role on Broadway.
But in the end, the Broadway show followed the edict of its title: They Took Him Out.